//    T12 loss smaller when chosen clearly preferred
//    T13 loss larger when rejected preferred
//    T14 gamma raises loss bar
//    T15 grad_w negative direction
//    T16 grad_l positive direction
//    T17 single train step decreases loss
//    T18 multi-step training converges
//    T19 preference accuracy correct
//    T20 preference accuracy wrong
